Mbupopia konthele yovanthu vali - ko , vapopiwa alo umwe novahipululi vomouye . — Lucas 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Jesus wapopiua novahoneki vomouye vo kotyita tyo tete no tya vali .
* Onkhalelo Jesus aipaelwe , ngetyi tyipopia ono Evandyeliu , yelifwa nawa nononkhalelo ova Roma ankho vaipaa ovanthu .
Tupu , ovipuka ovio viahipululwa monkhalelo yaviuka , vapopia alo umwe oviponyo vimwe viovalongwa va Jesus .
( Mateus 26 : 56 ; Lucas 22 : 24 - 26 ; João 18 : 10 , 11 ) Ovipuka ovio aviho , vilekesa nawa okuti ovahoneki vono Evandyeliu , ankho ovakuatyili monkhalelo vahoneka konthele ya Jesus .
Namphila ovanthu ovanyingi vetavela okuti Jesus wali - ko iya aipawa , mahi vamwe kavetavela okuti watutilisua .
Alo umwe ono apostolu mbae , po tete kavetavelele okuti wapindulua - po .
( Lucas 24 : 11 ) Mahi , apostolu novalongwa ovakuavo vetavela vala , etyi vamona Jesus ovikando ovinyingi .
Onthiki imwe , amonwa novanthu valamba po 500 . — 1 Coríntios 15 : 6 .
Ovalongwa va Jesus velipakele motyiponga tyokukuatwa nokuipawa , opo vapopile ovanthu aveho okuti Jesus watutilisua . Vapopilile alo umwe vana vemuipaele .
( Atos 4 : 1 - 3 , 10 , 19 , 20 ; 5 : 27 - 32 ) Inkha ovalongwa ovo aveho ankho vetyii nawa okuti Jesus tyotyili katutilisilwe , okuti ñgeno vapopile ngotyo nomutima wakola ?
Okunoñgonoka okuti tyotyili Jesus watutilisua , otyo tyikahi nokulunda ovanthu okukala Ovakristau , tunde kohale alo hono .
Etyi ono Evandyeliu mbupopia konthele yononkhia netutilo lia Jesus , tyilekesa nawa okuti olio , ehipululo lio tyotyili .
Inkha umbutanga nawa , mokala nonthumbi yokuti tyotyili ovipuka ovio viaendele - ko umwe .
Tupu , inkha unoñgonoka nawa oityi ovipuka ovio ankho vina okumonekela , matyipameka vali onthumbi yove tyina wamanoñgonoka omokonda yatyi ovipuka ovio viaendeleleko .
Tacitu , watyitua menima 55 P.K . , wahonekele okuti “ Kristu , una kuatuka enyina [ Ovakristau ] , wamonesilue ononkhumbi ononene na Posiu Pilatu , mokueenda kuoutumini wa Tibeliu . ”
Tupu , Jesus wapopiua na Suetoniu ( kotyita tyo tete ) , na Josefu omuhipululi omu Judeu ( kotyita tyo tete ) , na Pliniu o Moço , ankho omutumini wo Bitinia ( konthyimbi yotyita tyo tete ) .
( 1 Pedro 1 : 24 , 25 ) Tupu , katukevelela onondyale mba Jesus , mbuhoneke ovipuka vipondola okukuatesako ovanthu opo vetavele , avayumbu onthumbi m Jesus .
Petulu , umwe po no apostolu mba Jesus , wapopia konthele yetutilo lia Jesus okuti : ‘ Huku wemupindula - po monthiki ya tatu , iya emuyeke elilekese , hakovanthu - ko aveho , mahi o konombangi mbaholovonwa na Huku , kuonthue , vokualia nokunwa nae etyi apindulwa - po kononkhia . ’
O Evandyeliu ya Mateusi , itupopila okuti etyi onondyale vo nongeleya veiva okuti Jesus watutila , avaovola okutyilika ovalongwa vae opo vehetyiyandyanese . — Mateus 28 : 11 - 15 .
Okuti otyo tyilekesa okuti Jesus ankho uhanda ovanthu veheive okuti watutila ?
Au . Petulu watualako okupopia okuti : “ [ Jesus ] wetutuma okuivisa kovanthu nokuava oumbangi nombili , wokuti Ou oe una waholovonua na Huku opo akoyese vokuna omuenyo na vana vokuankhia . ”
Ovakristau vo tyotyili vatuaileko okuivisa , iya na hono otyo vekahi nokulinga . — Atos 10 : 42 .
“ Mokonda yomunthu wike vala [ Andau ] onkhali yanyingila mouye , iya onkhali yaeta ononkhia . ” — Romanos 5 : 12 .
Ove ñgeno wakumbulula ñgeni , inkha upulwa okuti : “ Uhanda okukala nomuenyo apeho ? ”
Ovanthu ovanyingi vapondola okuti vahanda , mahi hamwe vasoka okuti katyivilwa .
Mokonda vapopia okuti ovanthu vatyitwa , avankhi .
Pahe , soka ñgeno epulo olio lipilululwa , opulwa okuti : “ Ove uhanda okunkhia ? ”
Ovanthu ovanyingi vapondola okuti , au .
Ombimbiliya ipopia okuti Huku watunga ovanthu nehando liokukala nomuenyo apeho .
Yati : “ Wapaka alo umwe momutima wavo ehando liomuenyo wahapu . ” — Eclesiastes 3 : 11 .
Tyotyili , hono ovanthu kavatualako nomuenyo alo - loo .
Mahi okuti Huku una etyi alinga opo akuateseko ovanthu ?
Omakumbululo Ombimbiliya apameka unene , tupu alekesa nawa oityi Jesus amonesililwe ononkhumbi iya aipawa .
Ovikapitulu vitatu vio tete vio mukanda wa Genesis , vitupopila okuti Huku watungile ovalinepi vo tete , Andau na Eva nekevelelo liokukala nomuenyo wahapu . Huku evepopila oityi ankho vena okulinga opo vamone omuenyo oo .
Tupu , ovikapitulu ovio vipopia oñgeni vaanya okutavela ku Huku iya avapumbwa omuenyo wahapu .
Ehipululo olio otyipuka vala tyipopiwa , iya vamwe vetyitala ngatyina otyiso vala .
Mahi , ngetyi tyipopia ono Evandyeliu , tupu omukanda wa Gênesis ulekesa okuti , ehipululo olio oliotyotyili .
Etyi Andau ehetavelele , iya atyieta - tyi ?
Ombimbiliya ikumbulula okuti : “ Mokonda yomunthu wike vala [ Andau ] onkhali yanyingila mouye , iya onkhali yaeta ononkhia . Moluotyo , ononkhia mbeliyandyana kovanthu vatyo aveho , mokonda aveho valinga onkhali . ”
Mokonda yotyo , apumbua omuenyo wahapu , iya konyima ankhi .
Mokonda tuvana vae , tuapiñgana onkhali yae .
Mahi , okuti pena tyimwe Huku alinga opo akuateseko ovanthu ?
Pena etyi Huku alinga opo ovanthu vakakale nomuenyo wahakapwa - pwa vali Andau anyona .
Ombimbiliya momukanda wa Romanos 6 : 23 , ipopia okuti : “ Ofeto yonkhali ononkhia . ”
Otyo tyilekesa okuti , ononkhia mbaetwa nonkhali .
Tupu , nonthue tunkhia mokonda yonkhali .
Mahi hanthue - ko twapengesa , omokonda tuatyitwa - le nonkhali .
Mokonda Huku utuhole watuma Omona wae Jesus , opo ‘ etufetele - ko ononkhali ’ mbetu .
Ononkhia mba Jesus mbaikula ondyila yomuenyo wahapu
Onkhali nononkhia mbatuka komulume wike vala ankho uhena onkhali Andau , wehetavelele ku Huku . Ngotyo , ankho tyesukisa omunthu uhena nkhali opo etuyovole kononkhia .
Ombimbiliya ityihangununa nawa okuti : “ Ngotyo , mokonda yomunthu wike vala uhetavelele , ovanyingi vakala ovakuankhali , tupu mokonda ya wike vala wetavela , ovanyingi mavakala ovaviuki . ”
Watundile keulu , akala munthu uhena nkhali , * iya aipawa opo etuyovole .
Mokonda yotyo , pahe tupondola okukala noupanga na Huku , nekevelelo liokukakala nomuenyo wahapu komutwe .
Huku wapolele omuenyo wo Mona wae keulu , eupake meimo lia Maliya , iya kepondolo liospilitu sandu ya Huku , Jesus ahapiñgana onkhali ku Maliya . — Lucas 1 : 31 , 35 .
Okuti Huku Wepondolo Aliho ankho kapondola vala okuyeka ovana va Andau vakale nomuenyo uhapu ?
Inkha Huku wayekele - po otyitumino tyae tyokuti ondyambi yonkhali ononkhia , ñgeno ovanthu velipula inkha matetulula otyitateka otyo monkhalelo onkhuavo .
Mongeleka vapondola okulipula okuti : Ñgeno Huku wetyivila umwe okupunga nawa olie pokati kovana va Andau watokala okupewa omuenyo wahapu ?
Okuti ñgeno wayumbua umwe onthumbi yokuti ufuisapo omilao viae ?
Mokonda Huku uundapesa ovitumino viae opo etuyovole , otyo tyituavela onthumbi yokuti apeho malingi etyi tyaviuka .
Mokonda yononkhia mba Jesus , Huku waikula ondyila opo ovanthu vakakale nomueyo wahapu Momphangu Yombembwa pano pohi .
Tala onondaka mba Jesus mbuvasiwa mu João 3 : 16 mbati : “ Mokonda Huku una oluembia olunene novanthu , waava Omona wae wongunga , opo kese omunthu ukala nekolelo mwe ahakanyimueko , mahi akakale nomuenyo wahapu . ”
Ngotyo , ononkhia mba Jesus , kambulekesa vala okuti ouviuki wa Huku kauponyo , mahi haunene mbulekesa oluembia olunene ena novanthu aveho .
Mahi , oityi Jesus amonesililwe ononkhumbi iya aipawa ngetyi tyapopia ono Evandyeliu ?
